headline: Great Place To Work® and Fortune names Dow one of the World's Best Workplaces™ for the second consecutive year
summary: Great Place To Work® (GPTW) and Fortune magazine have honored Dow (NYSE: DOW) as one of the Fortune World's Best Workplaces™ in 2024 . This is the second consecutive year that Dow has earned this distinction.
